NBU</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>申請回鄉證去支那</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://bit.ly/2SY7wvc \" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2SY7wvc%20&h=4111c315&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>拍支那手機遊戲廣告</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://bit.ly/2GvAocS \" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2GvAocS%20&h=fe28cee5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://bit.ly/2LoQaVB \" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2LoQaVB%20&h=2318a362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://bit.ly/2UX8Ro2 \" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2UX8Ro2%20&h=3e7b16ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>代理支那手機遊戲《暴擊英雄-轟呀》</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://bit.ly/2Lwfidr \" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Lwfidr%20&h=60744928&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《暴擊英雄》（Attack Hero）是由广州簡悅遊戲旗下的獨立遊戲創作團隊&ldquo;CAP轟工作室&quot;研發的一款創意捲軸闖關遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>同支那公司合作</strong><br />\n剛剛更宣佈與奧柏中国（8148）結成伙伴，投資800萬元發展手遊業務，达狗成立達魂製作手機遊戲製作公司（Touch Fun Production）並出任行政總裁，首炮推出以达狗代言的手機遊戲《戰月勇者》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://bit.ly/2Gu3s4B \" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Gu3s4B%20&h=c5a5140a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n达狗（中）與奧栢中国集團、YES Culture、亞太電子競技協會及Gash Point等單位聯乘合作，今日正式啟動。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>畀兄弟踢爆講蝗語，达狗仲死雞撐飯蓋</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2rIjLAi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2rIjLAi&d=uKxilzV8Tp9rAPgAIDIpuYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=fd358220\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2rIjLAi</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/av4CNEe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fav4CNEe.png&h=f718dcd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uHiHejf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuHiHejf.jpg&h=ed8be837&s={SIZE}\"